WEBVTT

00:16:27.696 --> 00:16:30.871
(Pljesak)

00:16:30.895 --> 00:16:33.863
Imam tri stvari za reći, zar ne?

00:16:34.736 --> 00:16:36.562
Prvo, kao odgovor
na vaš prvi argument:

00:16:36.586 --> 00:16:40.179
nesumnjivo smo se promijenili,
sada želimo osobu koju ćemo voljeti,

00:16:40.203 --> 00:16:43.048
a tisućama godina,
morali smo se vjenčati za pravu osobu

00:16:43.072 --> 00:16:45.343
pravog porijekla i s pravim vezama.

00:16:45.367 --> 00:16:48.718
U biti, u mojim istraživanjima
od 5 000 ljudi godišnje

00:16:48.742 --> 00:16:50.868
pitam ih što traže.

00:16:50.892 --> 00:16:53.650
Svake godine,
preko 97 % ispitanika odgovara:

00:16:53.674 --> 00:16:54.884
EP: Popis traženog raste.

00:16:54.908 --> 00:16:56.068
HF: Pa ne baš.

00:16:56.092 --> 00:16:59.415
Preko 97% ljudi

00:16:59.439 --> 00:17:01.530
želi nekoga tko ih poštuje,